<header class="guide-header">
  <h1>Websites &amp; Guides</h1>
  <p class="guide-series">Privacy Resources</p>
</header>

<p class="resource-intro">Websites that can serve as your guides to personal privacy and security.</p>

<div class="resource-list">

<div class="resource-item">
  <h3><a href="https://www.privacyguides.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy Guides</a></h3>
  <p>One of the best online resources for all things digital privacy, anonymity and security. Regularly updated, this site contains guides, walkthroughs and recommended tools all presented in an easily readable and understandable way. I cannot recommend this site enough!</p>
</div>

<div class="resource-item">
  <h3><a href="https://inteltechniques.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">IntelTechniques</a></h3>
  <p>The website of Michael Bazzell, featuring his Extreme Privacy book series along with open-source intelligence (OSINT) tools, training, and resources for enhancing personal digital security and anonymity.</p>
</div>

<div class="resource-item">
  <h3><a href="https://ssd.eff.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Electronic Frontier Foundation's Surveillance Self-Defense</a></h3>
  <p>Resources from the non-profit <a href="https://www.eff.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">EFF</a> that fights to protect your digital privacy and security.</p>
</div>

<div class="resource-item">
  <h3><a href="https://www.techlore.tech/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Techlore</a></h3>
  <p>A small team educating people about digital rights, privacy, security and other important topics to push the world towards a safer and better internet.</p>
</div>

<div class="resource-item">
  <h3><a href="https://grapheneos.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GrapheneOS</a></h3>
  <p>The website of what is currently the most private and secure mobile operating system GrapheneOS. Provides an overview of features and an easy to follow installation guide.</p>
</div>

<div class="resource-item">
  <h3><a href="https://awesome-privacy.xyz/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Awesome-Privacy</a></h3>
  <p>Another website that showcases privacy respecting alternative software and services.</p>
</div>

<div class="resource-item">
  <h3><a href="https://digital-defense.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Digital Defence</a></h3>
  <p>A site that offers a comprehensive privacy and security checklist.</p>
</div>

</div>
